img_text: COMComplex Today BHAD BHABIE RESPONDED TO THE EMINEM COMPARISON When her fellow white rapper released his latest album, 'Kamikaze, some fans felt Em's flow on the track 'Not Alike' borrowed from Bhad Bhabie's on 'Hi Bich.' She responded positively to people pointing that out on social media in recent weeks and updated the final song on her mixtape with a nod to Slim Shady. I never dissed my mom to get some attention, take a second and listen, she says on 'Bhad Bhabie Story (Outro)' in what is a clear reference to Eminem's Cleanin' Out My Closet.' 15 HAD BHABIE
